					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5785759#post-3780050</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5785759/scp-3881#post-3780050</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 25 Apr 2018 06:04:35 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Golden506</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3700175</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I remember critting this. Its a far cry from before, despite that only being a few days. It still isn't my kind of thing, I really don't care about the characters, but I think its as good as its going to get.</p> <p>One other thing though, there was a small tonal error in the beginning of the description, I went ahead and fixed it for you. Obviously feel free to revert.</p> <p>EDIT: I came from the reddit post, read the first comment and it clicked. Still not my kind of thing, but I like it better.</p> <p>EDIT II: Okay Zyn reverted, I'll just say that I didn't think the segment &quot;and a few cosmetic alterations&quot; worked. It felt very informal to me, so maybe edit that.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5785759#post-3779919</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5785759/scp-3881#post-3779919</link>
				<description></description>
