				<wikidot:authorName>SirOnionbro</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3479638</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Glad to see more short skips. This is a perfect example of how to tell a story without needing to have a long and convoluted entry. Writing for both the entry itself and the interviews were great, got across the exact information they needed to; no more or less. +1.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
